    "text": [
        "The maps compare the layout of a southwest airport as it is with a proposed design next year.",
        "Overall, there will be considerable development of the airport over the year and it will be transformed from a simple one into a larger area with multiple functions.",
        "At the moment, the airport is divided into three parts by security passport control and passport control customs.  At the top is the rectangular boarding area with 8 gates scatter around and a walkway for passengers. At the bottom are areas for departures and arrivals with separate entrances. While there is nothing in the arrival area, a cafe locates in the right corner of the departure area and a check-in counter facing it.",
        "After the redevelopment, the boarding area will be expanded to a \"Y\" shape to accommodate 10 more gates and the walkway will be converted into a sky train.",
        "In the departure area, the check-in counter will be relocated to the right and the cafe to the bottom left. Where the check-in counter stands now, a bag drop will be built at the place.",
        "As to the arrival area, a cafe and an ATM will be added on its right side, and the bottom right corner will be expanded a little for a car hire centre. Both the areas will have extra entrances.",
        "Although the security passport control and passport control customs will not change, shops will be developed between the security and boarding area."
